data.title: Fred Savage at Emmy Awards
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.Photograph caption dated September 18, 1989 reads, "What do the Emmys mean to Fred Savage? 'A lot of pictures,' said 'The Wonder Years' star." Savage was nominated for the Outstanding Lead Actor in a Comedy Series Emmy for the 41st Annual Primetime Emmy Awards, held on September 17, 1989 at the Pasadena Civic Auditorium.
